enigma_edit.lua.data

Interface Indexed

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Typed
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MMTable, Table, Tiles

    public interface Indexed
extends Typed
    Interface to a lua table. This is implemented by the Table class itself and the multi-mode value MMTable.
